@adminAuth = YWRtaW5AdGVzdC5kZTpwYXNzd29yZA==

### GET alle Personen (Admin)
GET http://localhost:8080/api/persons
Accept: application/json
Authorization: Basic {{adminAuth}}


### POST gültige Person (201)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Max",
  "lastName": "Mustermann",
  "email": "max@test.de"
}

### POST ungültige Person (Validation → 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "",
  "lastName": "",
  "email": "abc"
}

### PATCH gültige Person (200)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/persons/{uuid}
If-Match: 0
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Max",
  "lastName": "Mustermann"
}

### PATCH ungültige Person (Validation → 400)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/persons/{uuid}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Max",
  "lastName": "Mustermann"
}

### PATCH unbekannte UUID (404)
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/persons/{uuid}
If-Match: 1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Test"
}

### DELETE – Person existiert nicht (404)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/persons/801199994147692596

###

### POST Person für DELETE-Test anlegen
POST http://localhost:8080/api/persons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "Delete",
  "lastName": "Test",
  "email": "delete@test.de"
}

###

### DELETE existierende Person
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/persons/{uuid}
###

### DELETE dieselbe Person erneut (404)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/persons/{uuid}

